  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>A buffet breakfast serving a selection of fresh items daily. </p>
<p>Half board and full board options are available for a supplement. These options are possible at all the three restaurants at the hotel. Guests can choose from the “à la carte menu” of all restaurants. Drinks are not included. For the Gourmet Restaurant pre booking is required</p>]]></cateringDescription>
