  <facilityDescription><![CDATA[<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Restaurants and Bars</strong></span> </p>
<p><strong>Restaurant <em>Corallina </em></strong>informal lunches and a rich buffet in the evening. From June to September there is a Pizzeria and guests can enjoy music and shows at the <span>poolside subtropical park for </span>Folies Royal.</p>
<p><strong>Restaurant <em>Il Gardino</em></strong> is open from June - September where guests can enjoy dinner on the terrace overlooking the sea </p>
<p><strong>Restaurant <em>Fiori di Murano</em></strong> dine beneath precious chandeliers with panoramic views. </p>
<p><strong>Bar <em>Delle Rose </em></strong>has live music in the evening. </p>
<p><strong>Bar<em> Corallina </em></strong>is open from April to October serving drinks and snacks by the pool.</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Pools &amp; Beaches </strong></span></p>
<ul>
<li><span>Private beach with sunbeds and umbrellas (payable locally from 2020)</span></li>
<li>Heated outdoor alt water swimming pool (28°C) is open from June to September (subject to weather conditions).</li>
</ul>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Spa</strong></span> </p>
<ul>
<li><span>Wellness centre with free access to wet room</span></li>
<li><span>Fitness and steam room</span></li>
<li><span>Treatments and massages (local charge)</span></li>
</ul>
<p><strong><u>Activities</u></strong></p>
<ul>
<li><span>Tennis court</span></li>
<li><span>Children's playground</span></li>
<li><span>Baby club - 07:00pm - 10:00pm from mid Jun - mid Sep</span></li>
<li><span>Children's playroom with animation programme during high season</span></li>
<li><span>Private swimming lessons for children aged 4-14 years old (payable locally)<br /></span></li>
</ul>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>General Facilities</strong></span></p>
<ul>
<li>Wifi</li>
<li>Garage (<span>€27 per night, payable locally and subject to availability)</span></li>
<li>Parking (<span>€17 per night, payable locally and subject to availability)</span><span></span></li>
</ul>]]></facilityDescription>
