  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p class="p1"><strong>Classic rooms</strong> are approximately, 20-34m² and have private bath or shower, air conditioning, television, minibar, safe and hairdryer. Each of the rooms are decorated in their own unique style. Baby cots free of charge and available on request. </p>
<p class="p1"><strong>Classic Rooms with Balcony and Sea View </strong>are about 25m².</p>
<p><strong>Junior Suites</strong> are approximately, 30-42m² and have a small sitting area. These rooms have a private bath or shower, air conditioning, television, minibar, safe and hairdryer. There is also WiFi available in the rooms. Each of the rooms are decorated in their own unique style. Junior Suites with balcony and sea view are available for a supplement.</p>
<p><strong>Single Occupancy </strong>Double rooms for single occupancy are available on request, please call to book. </p>]]></roomsDescription>
